{"data": [{"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "0_1775252119.303550", "card_id": "Q_2023407372723332647", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 131}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "苹果被曝高价扫荡全球手机内存，不惜牺牲利润锁死对手供应链，内存价格会再度暴涨吗？对安卓阵营冲击有多大？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "苹果公司被曝正在以极高价格收购市面上所有可用移动 DRAM 芯片 财联社 4 月 3 日消息，据韩国知情人士透露，苹果公司正在以极高的价格收购市面上所有可用的移动 DRAM 芯片，甚至不惜牺牲部分运营利润，这样可以阻止竞争对手获得足够的内存芯片。这一猜测与今年 1 月知名分析师郭明錤的想法几乎一致。当时，郭明錤就曾认为，内存涨价会影响苹果的毛利率，但吸收成本将有助于占领更大市场份额，且苹果可以通过服务来弥补损失。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-7c5e7d2cc22377fcd76c45fd93db5870_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "509 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2023407372723332647"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIzffzgv+7+algEAMaCTExOTAwOTE4NyDWvb3OBjAAOMwDQAByEzIwMjM0MDczNzI3MjMzMzI2NDd4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "1_1775252119.304404", "card_id": "Q_2021907413951882731", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 107}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么国外的家都喜欢暖光，但国内却喜欢冷白光？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-b3e7b69b360216caa169ff3ff89576c7_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "137 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2021907413951882731"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIzffzgv+7+algEAMaCTExODk1MzU3OCDk06fOBjAAOP8CQAFyEzIwMjE5MDc0MTM5NTE4ODI3MzF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "2_1775252119.304706", "card_id": "Q_2023391802560962717", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 260}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "贵州一县委书记闭幕致辞火了，全程 6 秒仅说两个字，这一极简致辞为何能火？折射出公众怎样的情绪？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "3 月 30 日傍晚，贵州黔东南州「州长杯」班超足球超级联赛榕江赛区闭幕式上，榕江县委书记徐勃走上球场，拿起话筒只说了「闭幕」二字，整个过程仅 6 秒，让现场的群众一愣，随后爆发出热烈掌声和笑声。 现场视频截图 4 月 3 日，极目新闻记者联系到视频中摆放话筒的组委会导演组的杨亚江，据他回忆，当时他话筒还没有完全摆好，县委书记徐勃就走过去说了「闭幕」两个字。下场后，徐勃与大家交流时表示，时间晚了，大家都累了，希望可以让大家早点回去休息，太晚路上不安全，他让大家赶快回家。 杨亚江还介绍，在 3 月 21 日的开幕式上，徐勃也只说了「开幕」两个字，原本预案是让他简单讲几句鼓励一下大家，再宣布开幕，但他只说了两个字，「没想到闭幕也这样，太简洁明了，出乎我们的预料，我肚子都笑疼了。」"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-3d45b3b38285d1e9dd1116836ff32ff9_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "134 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2023391802560962717"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIzffzgv+7+algEAMaCTExOTAwODQ1NyDWoL3OBjAAOPAEQAJyEzIwMjMzOTE4MDI1NjA5NjI3MTd4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "3_1775252119.305545", "card_id": "Q_2022998996315022600", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 50}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "港片常拍真实案件，1998 年索罗斯做空香港这么有名，怎么从来没拍成电影？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "[图片]"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-6677b126f4685bc40f6b1a52309788e4_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "123 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2022998996315022600"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIzffzgv+7+algEAMaCTExODk5MzUxOSCCxbfOBjAAOOEBQANyEzIwMjI5OTg5OTYzMTUwMjI2MDB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "4_1775252119.305863", "card_id": "Q_2000359413463159387", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 47}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待菲尔兹得主带头，千余数学家抵制在美举办国际数学家大会？对 2026 年国际数学家大会产生什么影响？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "法国数学会的官方通知:Title: La SMF n『ira pas à l』ICM de Philadelphie La SMF ne tiendra pas de stand à l『ICM de Philadelphie. En effet ni la délivrance de visas par le pays hôte, ni sa sécurité intérieure alors qu』y EST régulièrement évoquée la loi martiale, ne semblent garanties. Par ailleurs la SMF reste fondamentalement attachée à l『héritage de Benjamin Franklin, inséparable de la pensée rationnelle, et condamne la défiance envers la science et toute atteinte aux libertés académiques. (Motion du Conseil d』administration du 16 janvier 2026)"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-4442fc10cab0a26c05cae19fc29f83d4_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "103 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2000359413463159387"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIzffzgv+7+algEAMaCTExODI1OTA5OCDBi+7LBjAAOIoDQARyEzIwMDAzNTk0MTM0NjMxNTkzODd4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "5_1775252119.306716", "card_id": "Q_2023397131986170111", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 233}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价伊朗再次声称又击落一架美军 F35 战斗机？这次 F35 战斗机可能是如何被击落的？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "新华社德黑兰 4 月 3 日电 伊朗伊斯兰革命卫队公共关系部门 3 日发表声明说，防空系统在伊朗中部领空击落一架美国 F－35 战斗机。 声明说，该战斗机已被「完全摧毁并坠落」，战机已解体，飞行员下落不明。声明还说，这是伊斯兰革命卫队防空系统过去 12 小时内击落的第二架美国战机。 「这是我们对美国总统特朗普胡言乱语的首次回应。」声明写道。 伊朗媒体公布了战机解体碎片的照片，并表示飞行员生还几率很低。 伊朗伊斯兰革命卫队公共关系部门 2 日说，一架「先进的敌方战机」在霍尔木兹海峡附近的格什姆岛南部被伊方防空系统击中，该战机随后坠入波斯湾水域。美军中央司令部随后予以否认，称所有美军战斗机均处于「可查状态」。伊朗说击落又一架美军战机 - 新华网"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-d447839b7e4213576053abc2a6eb0ba7_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "102 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2023397131986170111"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIzffzgv+7+algEAMaCTExOTAwODYzNyDNqr3OBjAAOPoEQAVyEzIwMjMzOTcxMzE5ODYxNzAxMTF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "6_1775252119.307326", "card_id": "Q_2022610310935115479", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 34}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "新版软著申请表要求不得使用 AI 编写代码或文档，违者纳入征信记录，对行业有哪些影响？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "【转发】关于共同维护计算机软件版权登记良好生态的通知"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-f8de586178a3d440abb540c79fa5165a_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "102 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2022610310935115479"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIzffzgv+7+algEAMaCTExODk3ODIyNCCE8bHOBjAAOEhABnITMjAyMjYxMDMxMDkzNTExNTQ3OXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "7_1775252119.307651", "card_id": "Q_2023060151108641565", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 161}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待日本埼玉县拉面店贴出「用餐时禁止看手机，违者驱逐且不退款」？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "近日，日本春日部市人气拉面店「煮干乱舞」因严禁食客边吃边玩手机引发争议。店主称此举是为了保证细面的「最佳赏味期」，并由于曾有顾客将手机放调料盒上导致卫生担忧。律师称「事前告知即契约成立」。这种将社交礼仪转化为强硬法律契约的做法，是匠心守护还是对消费者的过度霸凌？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-e787fc2b702bff30250c07f8f4219565_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "100 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2023060151108641565"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIzffzgv+7+algEAMaCTExODk5NjQwNCD2trjOBjAAOKcCQAdyEzIwMjMwNjAxNTExMDg2NDE1NjV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "8_1775252119.308005", "card_id": "Q_2022998422685312960", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 70}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "时隔 57 年人类再靠近月球，为什么人类要花费大量人力物力去探索月球？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-80306c345fe059b13faa3d2614beeb16_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "99 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2022998422685312960"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIzffzgv+7+algEAMaCTExODk5MzM5NyD5w7fOBjAAOL0BQAhyEzIwMjI5OTg0MjI2ODUzMTI5NjB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "9_1775252119.308234", "card_id": "Q_2023328039937786913", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 15}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "特朗普正式对进口专利药品征收 100% 关税，为何其还能收关税，此举会对全球创新药市场产生多大影响？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "财联社 4 月 3 日讯（编辑 黄君芝）据央视新闻报道，白宫当地时间周四（2 日）宣布，美国政府将对部分进口药品加征 100% 的关税。 根据白宫当天发布的一份公告，美国总统特朗普签署一份文件，依据《1962 年贸易扩展法》第 232 条款，美国将对进口专利药和制药成分加征 100% 的关税。这一措施同时提供豁免或下调关税的路径，旨在迫使制药企业与白宫就药品价格和产业回流等达成协议。 敲定 100% 关税！特朗普「剑指」进口专利药及制药成分美国政府高级行政官员透露：除非制药商已签署药品定价协议，或是同意在美生产该产品，否则美国将对进口专利药品征收 100% 关税。特朗普政府宣布将对品牌药征收最高 100% 的关税"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "96 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2023328039937786913"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIzffzgv+7+algEAMaCTExOTAwMzk2NiD0qbzOBjAAOCxACXITMjAyMzMyODAzOTkzNzc4NjkxM3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "10_1775252119.308875", "card_id": "Q_2023064985580893986", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 307}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "外交部回应「伊朗是否向中国寻求安全保障」，表示中方支持一切有利于和平的努力，释放哪些信号？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "4 月 2 日，外交部发言人毛宁主持例行记者会。 有外媒记者提问，有报道称，伊朗已向中国寻求安全保障，如果这些保障能够提供，美以伊或能达成停火协议。请问伊朗是否已向中国提出过此类请求？中国是否已作出回应？ 「伊朗战事爆发以来，中方一直积极致力于促和止战，中巴两国外长会见的情况，我们已经发布了消息，你可以查阅。」毛宁说，我可以告诉你的是，中方支持一切有利于和平的努力，我们也愿意同各方加强沟通和协调，为恢复中东地区的和平继续发挥作用。 外媒称伊朗已向中国寻求安全保障，外交部回应"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-361546b71010d594e66082919922bcb4.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "95 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2023064985580893986"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIzffzgv+7+algEAMaCTExODk5NjYzMSD3v7jOBjAAONwFQApyEzIwMjMwNjQ5ODU1ODA4OTM5ODZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "11_1775252119.309535", "card_id": "Q_1947271556913934593", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 27}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "和牛的牛杂卖给哪里了？还是直接扔了？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "牛内脏 牛眼睛 牛枪牛宝 牛舌头之类的"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-46ada2cc4f43bdea5b64acb4482241e2_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "94 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/1947271556913934593"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIzffzgv+7+algEAMaCTExNjQ3ODEzMCDVx+nFBjAAOG9AC3ITMTk0NzI3MTU1NjkxMzkzNDU5M3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "12_1775252119.309853", "card_id": "Q_593462158", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 184}, "target": {"ti